      "content": "but there is no \"way forward\" when the foundation is gone. you don't get it. it wasn't just a mistake, it was my whole identity. once you realize the core of who you are is a lie, there's no rebuilding. it's just a loop of pretending to be something that isn't there. there's just this massive, empty silence where my purpose used to be.",
